    {"id":"demo-climatemesh","label":"ClimateMesh lead — 1.8M-param VICReg+pred world model","raw":"Lead researcher on ClimateMesh. The 1.8M-parameter VICReg+pred SOTA variant beats 100× larger weather foundation models on 5-day forecast retrieval. Phase 4 pre-paper as of 2026-04-30."},
    {"id":"demo-diff-forecast","label":"Active: Diff-Forecast plan (Qwen-Sky SFT)","raw":"Active research plan Diff-Forecast — un-parked 2026-04-26. Pipeline reproduces the paper; SFT regression discovered, recipe sweep in progress before scaling. Trains Qwen-Sky on AWS."},
    {"id":"demo-skydiff","label":"Active: SkyDiff E2 (diffusion-LM + LoRA)","raw":"SkyDiff E2 ablation status update 2026-04-29: both tracks positive. Track 1 v2→v3 reveals capacity tradeoff with full-FFN coverage; Track 2 is now a design-iteration story with positive control."},
    {"id":"demo-stack","label":"Trains on AWS (4× A100) → W&B → HuggingFace","raw":"Compute stack: AWS GPUs (mostly 4× A100 for Phase 2 trajectory experiments), W&B for logging, HuggingFace for artifact persistence. Training runs are usually overnight."},
    {"id":"demo-manim","label":"Manim style: 3Blue1Brown classic palette","raw":"Preferred Manim visualization style is 3Blue1Brown classic palette. Uses Manim CE for explainer animations on the team blog."},
    {"id":"demo-northstar","label":"North-star: 'models anyone can hand to a meteorologist'","raw":"Long-term goal: build climate models that working meteorologists can use without an ML degree."},
    {"id":"demo-hackathon","label":"Currently in: Hermes Creative Hackathon (deadline 2026-05-03)","raw":"Active hackathon entry: Hermes Agent Creative Hackathon (Nous Research × Kimi/Moonshot). $15k Main + $5k Kimi tracks. Deadline EOD Sun 2026-05-03."},
    {"id":"demo-essays","label":"Writes mini-essays on agentic systems","raw":"MiniEssays series. 'Agentic Tool Calling' (Dec 2025) — argues tool use is the most important pattern in modern agentic systems for going beyond knowledge cutoffs."}
  ]
